Production: Written by Charles Burnley, it is directed by Jon Keeyes. The film originally had the working title The Last Girl. The film is produced by Jordan Yale Levine, Jordan Beckerman, and Michael J. Rothstein for Yale, as well as Richard Bolger and Conor Barry from Hail Mary Pictures, and Richard Clabaugh.
Alice Eve, Shelley Hennig and Antonio Banderas joined the cast in June 2022.
Principal photography took place in Ireland and was completed in September 2022.
Release: The film was released in the United States on January 19, 2024.
